---
title: Chicken, Tomato & Mushroom Stew with Dark Meat Chicken & Buttered Noodles
description: Sometimes, all you need is a cozy, warm bowl of stew—and in those moments, this is one you’ll want to reach for. Dark meat chicken is super juicy and flavorful, especially when paired with umami-rich mushrooms and tomato. To complete the meal, you’ll serve it over buttered cavatappi noodles—perfect for soaking up any extra gravy in your bowl!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6772d224d8e11bf886853900-971f5aa9.jpeg
